headline: /C O R R E C T I O N -- Oceania Cruises/
summary: Oceania Cruises®, the world's leading culinary- and destination-focused cruise line, has announced that the installation of the world's first and largest satellite constellation, Starlink, has been completed on all ships, providing all guests with high-speed, unlimited WiFi included as part of the cruise fare.
